 <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
  To do the sign for "don't mind"
  <font face="Arial">
   touch the 
	tip of your index finger to your nose, then sweep the tip of the index 
	finger in an arch until it is pointing down and forward.
  This sign can be used to ask, "Would it be okay if I..."
   <br/>
  </font>
  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   DON'T MIND? = "Do you 
	mind if...?"
   <br/>
   <br/>
   <img border="0" src="../../gifs/d/dont-mind-1.gif" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto" width="480"/>
   <img border="0" src="../../gifs/d/dont-mind-2.gif" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto" width="480"/>
   <img border="0" src="../../gifs/d/dont-mind-3.gif" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto" width="480"/>
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   <font face="Arial">
    <img border="0" height="205" src="../../gifs-animated/dontmind.gif" width="195"/>
   </font>
  </p>
  <font face="Arial">
   <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1" width="50%"/>
  </font>
  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
