  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   <br/>
   This next version (which uses less facial expression) can be used to reply, 
	"I don't mind."
   <br/>
   (But realistically, I'd just sign "OK," "SURE," or "FINE" instead of "I 
	don't mind.")
   <br/>
   <br/>
