  <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   Notes:
   <br/>
   The sign "don't mind" can be used to mean "I don't care." But there is 
	another sign that more specifically expresses the concept of "I don't care," 
	see: "
   <a href="dont-care.htm">
